The issues that are created by Atlassian Support Tools into ServiceDesk are created with the Timezone specified in the application itself and ignoring the timezone preference of the user that is reporting.
Additionally, in the SD itself, there is no option to update the timezone for the issue.

This is important when I am creating an SD request out of e.g. Bamboo, where my customer is running GMT-9 and I am in GMT+1 and am expecting the answers now, and not in the next 12h, letting me answer to questions after next 10h.

